lead_paragraph: The New York Times: Last call at the Miss Albany Diner, a chrome-clad fixture in the state capital since the 1940s. Say farewell to Cliff's Ugly Eggs (dark with anchovies and mushrooms) and Mad Irish Toast (French toast and Irish whiskey). -- Patrick Farrell
